=== Subsidiary Shrines ===  

'''Within the precincts'''  
* Tadasu Shrine  
* Itsukushima Shrine  
* Otoshi Shrine  

'''Outside the precincts'''  
* Ogo Shrine  
  * Location: Kawaminami, Yufuin-chō, Yufu City  
  * The grounds contain many giant cedars, including the nationally designated natural monument “Great Cedar of Ogo Shrine,” over 1,000 years old and 38 meters tall (designated August 9, 1934).  

* Kerisaki Gongen Shrine  
  * Location: Nakagawa, Yufuin-chō, Yufu City  
  * Enshrines the deity associated with the Kerisaki legend.  

